Date: Wed,  9 May 2007 09:59:17 +0200
From: Jens Axboe <>
Subject: [PATCH 3/10] libata: convert to using sg helpers
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
X-Mailing-List: linux-kernel@vger.kernel.org
X-Lkml-Link: https://lkml.org/lkml/2007/5/9/56

This converts libata to using the sg helpers for looking up sg
elements, instead of doing it manually.
Signed-off-by: Jens Axboe <jens.axboe@oracle.com>
---
